string.name: wp_test_results_activity_title

string.name: wp_test_results_no_data
string.context: Displays when there are no test results to view

string.name: wp_test_results_no_ordering_provider
string.context: Message shown on test result summary as replacement for provider name when no provider is listed

resources.string: There was a problem loading all of your test results. Tap for details.

string.name: wp_test_results_h2g_error_popup_title
string.context: Title in error popup that is shown when an error was encountered while loading results from other organizations

string.name: wp_test_results_accessibility_name_date
string.context: Voiceover text for test result cell where %1$@ is the name of test result and %2$@ is the date it was resulted.

string.name: wp_test_results_accessibility_abnormal
string.context: Text that would be prepended to the voice over for the cell if the test is abnormal. %1$@ is the test result name and date.

string.name: wp_test_results_accessibility_unread
string.context: Text that would be prepended to the voice over for the cell if the test is unread. %1$@ is the test result name and date.

string.name: wp_test_results_accessibility_ordering_provider
string.context: Voice over text for the cell with the ordering provider appended. %1$@ is the name of the test. %2$@ is the provider's name.

string.name: wp_test_results_accessibility_cell_external
string.context: Appended voice over text for the cell with external organization info. %1$@ is the text of the test result. %2$@ is the external organization name.

string.name: wp_test_results_accessibility_preview_text
string.context: Voice over text for the cell with external organization info appended. %1$@ is the text of the test result. %2$@ is the test results preview.
